    <item>
      <title>关税战中干邑白兰地被中国免税渠道封锁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/cognac-blocked-from-duty-free-channels-in-china-in-tariff-battle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[干邑生产商被禁止通过中国的免税渠道分销法国白兰地，这显然加剧了北京与欧盟之间的关税争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/cognac-blocked-from-duty-free-channels-in-china-in-tariff-battle</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 10:32:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯称将按时释放人质，避免战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/israeli-minister-expects-hamas-to-honor-hostage-release-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯表示，将于周六按计划释放人质，放弃了无限期推迟的威胁，这一决定使人们对最初为期六周的加沙停火协议的持久性产生了怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/israeli-minister-expects-hamas-to-honor-hostage-release-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 09:48:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰对泽连斯基批评者波罗申科实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/ukraine-sanctions-former-president-opposition-leader-poroshenko</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着乌克兰与俄罗斯达成不愉快的和平协议的可能性越来越大，为新的选举奠定了基础，乌克兰对该国反对派领导人、前总统彼得·波罗申科进行了制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/ukraine-sanctions-former-president-opposition-leader-poroshenko</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 09:03:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与普京通话后，被边缘化的欧洲寻求在乌克兰发挥作用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/europe-demands-role-in-ukraine-talks-after-trump-putin-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普与弗拉基米尔·普京的通话令欧洲领导人措手不及，他们坚称，在美国总统表示已同意与俄罗斯总统普京通过谈判结束乌克兰战争后，他们不应该被排除在外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/europe-demands-role-in-ukraine-talks-after-trump-putin-call</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 07:50:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税问题导致风险偏好减弱，美元缩减跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/dollar-falls-as-trump-putin-talk-over-end-to-war-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，今日将实施对等关税，这抑制了市场对高风险资产的兴趣，并引发了人们对通胀可能进一步加速的担忧，随后美元缩减了跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/dollar-falls-as-trump-putin-talk-over-end-to-war-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 05:03:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普“令人震惊”的贸易局势令印尼寻求新协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/indonesia-seeks-new-deals-as-shocking-trump-tariffs-roil-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼贸易部副部长迪亚·罗罗·埃斯蒂·维迪亚·普特里表示，随着全球保护主义愈演愈烈，印尼正寻求实现市场多元化，同时也采取措施保护本土制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/indonesia-seeks-new-deals-as-shocking-trump-tariffs-roil-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 02:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
